*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZBK_P009
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&Normal Screen-PBO ve PAI-GUI Title-GUI Status
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zbk_p009.

* Screen olu#madan önce PBO(Process Before Output) bu yap#da ekran aç#lmadan önce yap#lmak istenen i#lemler gerçekle#ir.
* Screen ça##r#ld#ktan sonra ise PAI(Process After Input) yap#s#n# kullan#r#z.

*DATA: lv_num1 TYPE i. "Display Object List button or CTRL + SHITF + F5 --> FIELDS

START-OF-SELECTION. "Display Object List button or CTRL + SHITF + F5 --> EVENTS

*PERFORM form1.
*FORM form1 . "Display Object List button or CTRL + SHITF + F5 --> SUBROUTINES
*ENDFORM.

  CALL SCREEN 0100.

*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Module STATUS_0100 OUTPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&Ekran aç#lmadan önce.
MODULE status_0100 OUTPUT.
  SET PF-STATUS 'STATUS_0100'. "GUI statusleri yazaca##m#z alan.
  SET TITLEBAR 'TITLE_0100'. "TITLE k#sm#n# yazaca##m#z alan.
ENDMODULE.

*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Module  USER_COMMAND_0100  INPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*       text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
*Ekran aç#ld#ktan sonra.
MODULE user_command_0100 INPUT.
  IF  sy-ucomm EQ '&BACK'.
    LEAVE TO SCREEN 0.
  ENDIF.
ENDMODULE.
